{"tid":2305781,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過帶發情緊既貓女去SPCA絕育?","createTime":"2020-11-30T02:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T20:04:57.000Z","uid":234482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a647827e1dbe78840ca2ac8dc151371e6cae36d1","tid":2305781,"uid":234482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T02:57:25.000Z","msg":"最近8個月既貓女突然第一次發情，11月月頭先打完針，<br />\n就即刻book12月絕育，點知絕育前唔夠一個禮拜就發情，<br />\n而家都唔知仲好唔好繼續絕育，因為上網見到好多話發情緊絕育會更高風險，<br />\n但SPCA又話絕對唔會有問題，都唔知信唔信得過~<br />\n而加如果再改期已經要到1月，但好驚果陣又發情緊依個情況無限loop"},{"pid":"3e6e46e9de69c344d8af6045e0539b171b1ee0c3","tid":2305781,"uid":7854,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T02:59:41.000Z","msg":"肯定唔得 充左血 想靠害?"},{"pid":"12244b0c4f492f6d26cf44bcbfcedf05b1c7595b","tid":2305781,"uid":213607,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T03:01:13.000Z","msg":"你屌完舒緩下佢再去做會好啲"},{"pid":"61a588163091672937dfc40fac5d1a18853b2ebe","tid":2305781,"uid":21308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T03:04:30.000Z","msg":"我個陣都係發情做絕育 不過唔係spca<br />\n佢晚晚叫 醫生話做得就做 始終醫生專業"},{"pid":"1d2208f6ba6ac1cfd6090c07e23e94c8516bab45","tid":2305781,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T04:52:12.000Z","msg":"好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />發下情都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲慘過毒撚有得打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bdaac8bdf4d06e59621ba01a824eed15a1d3d46","tid":2305781,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T05:28:46.000Z","msg":"發情都要絕育<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫下春唔得咩???"},{"pid":"081cd52b28f6eb35bda651ae51ba7ec8780ca424","tid":2305781,"uid":14486,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T05:32:30.000Z","msg":"連生命本能都冇埋<br />\n成世都係玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70fbc7f98099dbe0f036f17856b6e553eaf076e3","tid":2305781,"uid":155818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T05:33:56.000Z","msg":"你試下扯緊嗰時比人閹左點諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2585b8be81ef789790e8d95c98b82a6ca79dc2","tid":2305781,"uid":159582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T08:57:45.000Z","msg":"俾啲貓草佢hi下先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b14ce7992fdfec621fe7a767e7bc23cc94af91","tid":2305781,"uid":383842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:51:00.000Z","msg":"打過去問下姑娘醫生 可能會要你另外加錢 應該冇咩特別"},{"pid":"c67e7a1e516eab26b7299799df7cff4ffece8782","tid":2305781,"uid":318978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T00:21:35.000Z","msg":"應該要絕<br />\n啲人成日話絕育唔人道<br />\n但其實佢有生理需要但又唔可以解決仲慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話唔應該絕啲人有冇喺佢地角道諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋絕左後某啲病嘅機會低啲 例如乳癌<br />\n<br />\n絕育應該早做好 貓咪會復原得快啲"},{"pid":"cbf241b1f36c6bdbfaac93e19de5d7dd09d90099","tid":2305781,"uid":202942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T19:11:33.000Z","msg":"我有呀 去左西貢spca絕育 嗰陣貓女發緊情 但個醫生話ok 最後個傷口都埋得好好<br />\n我諗係睇醫生 有經驗嘅就可以做"},{"pid":"19e50f1d0b0012b5c2a40cb47827112c4a57fc25","tid":2305781,"uid":122915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T23:52:50.000Z","msg":"我好記得上網贂過好多資料話發緊情唔好做<br />\n發完先再絕<br />\n原因一來係充血 二來係發緊時如果女既話子宮會難搞好多 有機會手術失敗仲有生命危險<br />\n我建議你自己做多少少RESEARCH 搵埋英文SOURCE先<br />\n穩陣起見唔好懶"},{"pid":"4f2f0066ecb4d595b48677c9fbf7a09c48cdc05d","tid":2305781,"uid":58653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T20:04:57.000Z","msg":"貓女可以365日幾時想發情就發，所以發緊情去做絕育係無問題。不過因為發緊情啲血管會擴張，有機會流血會流多少少咁解，同埋通常都要加錢。"}]}